3. Describe the following motivations or desired outcomes of threat actors.
Fraud	
Fraud-motivated threat actors seek money through means like identity theft or credit card fraud.
Sabotage	Threat actors motivated by sabotage want to disrupt an organization for strategic reasons.  This may involve disrupting critical infrastructure, interrupting services, or causing damage to systems.
Vandalism	Threat actors motivated by vandalism aim to destroy or deface digital assets, like websites, to cause harm.
Theft	Threat actors motivated by theft want to access and take valuable assets, like sensitive information, for personal gain or to sell.

